# Clay Design System

All UI in this project MUST follow the Clay design system. Never deviate.

## Colors

- **Background**: Warm Cream `#faf9f7` — never cool white or gray
- **Text**: Clay Black `#000000`
- **Secondary text**: Warm Silver `#9f9b93`
- **Tertiary text**: Warm Charcoal `#55534e`
- **Border (primary)**: Oat `#dad4c8` — always warm, never neutral gray
- **Border (light)**: Oat Light `#eee9df`
- **Accent green**: Matcha 300 `#84e7a5`, 600 `#078a52`, 800 `#02492a`
- **Accent cyan**: Slushie 500 `#3bd3fd`, 800 `#0089ad`
- **Accent gold**: Lemon 400 `#f8cc65`, 500 `#fbbd41`, 700 `#d08a11`
- **Accent purple**: Ube 300 `#c1b0ff`, 800 `#43089f`
- **Accent pink**: Pomegranate 400 `#fc7981`

## Dark Theme (warm-inverted)

- Background: `#1a1815`, Surface: `#23201b`, Border: `#3a362f`
- Text: `#f0ede8`, Secondary: `#9f9b93`

## Typography

- **Primary font**: `'DM Sans', Arial, sans-serif` (substitute for Roobert)
- **Mono font**: `'Space Mono', monospace`
- **Headings**: weight 600, tight letter-spacing (e.g. -0.4px at 20px)
- **UI/Buttons**: weight 500
- **Body**: weight 400
- **Uppercase labels**: 12px, weight 600, `text-transform: uppercase`, letter-spacing 1.08px

## Shadows

- **Clay Shadow**: `rgba(0,0,0,0.1) 0px 1px 1px, rgba(0,0,0,0.04) 0px -1px 1px inset, rgba(0,0,0,0.05) 0px -0.5px 1px`
- **Hard Offset (hover)**: `rgb(0,0,0) -7px 7px`
- Never use standard blur-based box shadows

## Border Radius Scale

- Sharp: 4px (inputs, ghost buttons)
- Standard: 8px (small elements)
- Card: 12px (cards, buttons)
- Feature: 24px (feature cards, panels)
- Section: 40px (large containers)
- Pill: 1584px (CTAs, pill buttons)

## Component Patterns

- **Cards**: white bg, `1px solid #dad4c8`, 12–24px radius, clay-shadow
- **Buttons**: Use `.clay-btn-solid` (black bg, white text) or `.clay-btn-white` (white bg, oat border, clay-shadow)
- **Inputs**: `1px solid #dad4c8`, 8px radius, matcha-600 focus border
- **Dividers**: `border-top: 1px solid #dad4c8`
- **Labels**: Use `.clay-label` class (uppercase, 12px, weight 600, tracking 1.08px)
- **Modals**: Fixed overlay with `bg-clay-black/30`, centered `.clay-card`
- Mix solid and dashed borders for visual variety

## Do NOT

- Use cool gray backgrounds or borders (`#ccc`, `#ddd`, `#f5f5f5`)
- Use standard blur shadows
- Use border-radius < 12px on feature cards
- Skip warm oat borders in favor of neutral ones
